Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶...要是一直開著的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再怎麼傻也是會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(日本有傻瓜不會感冒的說法)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會冷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的還很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為才剛進二月而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店裡有很多雜誌上登著巧克力的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為吃了巧克力就會暖和起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為情人節就快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節?

Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:40.69,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組

Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:35.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:35.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:40.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:40.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:51.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:51.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:02:00.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:02:00.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:07.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:07.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:18.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:18.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:41.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:41.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

