Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:03:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...踏上旅途的人.]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月14日是情人節呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要在艾草保育園辦情人節會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要在保育園辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保育園不辦的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有的保育園會辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在日本也就是送巧克力的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 書裡也是這麼寫的 所以我們也辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生給男生送嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是女生送巧克力給喜歡的男生的日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?情人節是這麼回事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 最近反過來的好像也有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還真是什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給喜歡的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦辦看吧 情人節會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師 最近又好像總在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常難受 卻又努力不讓別人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓清花老師在情人節那天能精神一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在園裡已經沒有餘錢來辦這種活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru會分給我們一些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上去店裡商量了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做巧克力需要的材料用兼職來換就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 去蛋糕店chiroru幫忙做事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換來保育園的大家做巧克力需要的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這樣跟人家交涉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有什麼地方行不通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼職安排太滿 給chiroru幫忙恐怕很難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜裡都安排了工地的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙的事情就我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始每天保育園放學以後去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到情人節那天為止就行了 店長這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了情人節 小鳩會加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!加油加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩要在園裡辦情人節會?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個溫柔的孩子呢 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會繼續努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想這樣拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天已經到關店的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?已經這麼晚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個 有什麼其他的能幫忙的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離情人節還有兩天 你已經幫了不少忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 能把外面的看板收進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又以這種奇怪的方式掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回又不是海上之類的 有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次可差一點就要死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是女孩子!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界白饅頭一樣的東西會不會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這個人叫做黑鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒...誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我叫法伊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上這位是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那 說話也不要緊的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看她一點都不吃驚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說話的玩偶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想摸魚到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫五百祗先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫柯那 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那遊樂園的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們正在旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人和一莫柯那一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一莫柯那?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那的數量單位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 哪有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑鋼和五百祗先生的聲音真的很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的黑鋼 藍藍的小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住嘴 白饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們是旅行到此?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在書裡讀到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行要在很多地方過夜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定在哪裡過夜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什麼地方能讓我們留宿的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有這個世界的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在身上帶的大概不能用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很發愁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過沒有女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以露宿也沒問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那就是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡能夠區分性別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果發愁的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來我家住一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 有房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過被褥只有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家疊在一塊的睡話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是又有塊頭比較大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上邊的被子和下邊的褥子分開來蓋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一套被褥就是說 一個人住?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還有五百祗先生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話越發不妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭敬不如從命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我說你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有五百祗先生保護的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 向小鳩家 go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,go go的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有什麼打算的吧 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這麼酷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼想 也許還真的什麼都沒想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保育園休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早一定要去chiroru的說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經叫過你許多次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩睡的很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不管房間裡有什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點都不變呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我這就要出門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要在意 只管呆在房間裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩是要去蛋糕店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了獲得情人節用來做巧克力的材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 作為留我們住的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕店啊 這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君 你陪她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做料理很厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑作為蛋糕店員的話有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑和我去其他地方打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籌集資金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫柯那呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和五百祗先生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得和你很親近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親密的兩個人的連攜play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親密個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生情不自禁地嫉妒莫柯那的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美 那個男孩子是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是小鳩的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝布偶的樣子 莫柯那很擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生真的非常手巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟能生巧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我練習了多少次都沒法包好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要總想一次塞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你吶 不要唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生你們 一直都在旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 並不是有目的地的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是次把不斷旅行作為目的的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說還沒有決定去哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要決定很難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在同一個地方呆多久都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等著不知下次何時會回來的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...有一個想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為去到那個地方有什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說去到那裡以後有你想見到的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見的...人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...想見的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是坐在那裡而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以是作為看板莫柯那的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕店那邊如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生很手巧 店長也一直誇獎他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也說了這衣服很少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 衣服啊 我們也很辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人問這是COSPLAY嗎什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在這個世界是不是算是COSPLAY呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才弄得解釋不清的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟只有一天 沒有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你肯收下我們會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是給你留我們住的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會為艾草保育園使用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這個耳飾亮起來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要前往下一個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我們住下來真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是兩天一夜 但是很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒幫到各位什麼忙實在是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小鳩她啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 好像十分不安定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 好美的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是莫柯那最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在其他世界只能祝福她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也包含我們的份在內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你照顧好她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去到就好了 你想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從其他世界來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為世界並不只有這個人間界而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界 地界 異界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這些可能還有其他許多不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望小狼先生他們下一個去到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是等待他們的人所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(情人節會 加油)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 那個借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩真的很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩你那個的形狀真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是想做成星星的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是海星嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?像海星先生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了巧克力她還給了我錢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連裝巧克力的包裝盒還有卡片都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 沒有勉強自己就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 義男君要把巧克力送給誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽 還有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要送給媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有送一份給小鳩也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要把最好的巧克力送給最喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩要把最好的送給誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩那傢伙 有留我那份的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.73,0:22:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩她...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒多少時間了...

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:11.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}なくしたものと あつめたものの狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:11.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所失與所得的縫隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:20.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの笑顔　落ちていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:20.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遺落著你的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:26.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}届きそうで　届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:26.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}彷彿伸手可及卻又遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}飛んでゆけるわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飛又飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}笑わせてあげたいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我只是想讓你有更多笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}役立たずのこの翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:43.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}這沒用的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}何のためにあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}到底為什麼存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの傍で笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:55.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我會在你身邊微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:00.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私に出来ること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:00.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}這是我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:07.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}暖めるだけでもいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:07.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕給你一絲溫暖也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}せめて包みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}至少想包容著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:19.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}気付くの　そのための翼と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:19.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}終於發覺 雙翼是為此存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:27.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}今こそわたし　笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:27.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所以我現在 在微笑

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.17,0:24:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...春天的腳步聲.]
